&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About HumanSignal&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Real-world data is the competitive edge in AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;HumanSignal is a human data partner for companies building AI models and products. Our customers ship better AI, faster, because we partner with their researchers from real-world data creation to annotation to delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;We design and create datasets from scratch, recruit and manage the domain experts who evaluate model output, and run everything through our own platform, Label Studio, the open-source standard for data labeling and evaluation, used by over 1 million practitioners worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;We specialize in the operationally complex: real-world data collection, multimodal pipelines, and multi-step workflows. Advanced ML and AI teams use our enterprise platform to run their own data factories, and our services team to extend their reach where in-house capacity runs out.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you want to do work that materially shapes how the next generation of AI products gets built, we&#39;d love to talk.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 4px 0; padding: 0; color: #1d1c1d;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Get Paid to Review Car Damage Photos — Flexible, Remote, Freelance Work&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Looking for a flexible way to earn extra money on the side? We&#39;re hiring freelance contractors to work on a photo review project for a leading European insurance company — and you can do it from anywhere in the EU, on your own schedule.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;What you&#39;ll be doing:&lt;/strong&gt; Reviewing photos of damaged vehicles and marking the affected areas — things like scratches, dents, cracks, and missing parts — and identifying which part of the car is involved (door, bumper, hood, fender, etc.). Your work directly helps insurance customers receive faster, fairer damage assessments. Full training is provided through clear written guidelines with visual examples.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;This is a great fit if you have a background in:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin: 4px 0 4px 24px; padding: 0;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 2px 0; padding: 0; color: #1d1c1d;&quot;&gt;Auto insurance claims or appraisal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 2px 0; padding: 0; color: #1d1c1d;&quot;&gt;Auto body or mechanic work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 2px 0; padding: 0; color: #1d1c1d;&quot;&gt;Car dealership or parts experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 2px 0; padding: 0; color: #1d1c1d;&quot;&gt;Any field where identifying vehicle damage and parts is second nature&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 4px 0; padding: 0; color: #1d1c1d;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;The details:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin: 4px 0 4px 24px; padding: 0;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 2px 0; padding: 0; color: #1d1c1d;&quot;&gt;Must be based in the EU&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 2px 0; padding: 0; color: #1d1c1d;&quot;&gt;100% remote, work at your own pace&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 2px 0; padding: 0; color: #1d1c1d;&quot;&gt;Pays roughly €11/hour&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 2px 0; padding: 0; color: #1d1c1d;&quot;&gt;Project volume is expected to be substantial, with strong potential for increased workload and extended project duration as things scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 2px 0; padding: 0; color: #1d1c1d;&quot;&gt;Freelance/contract work — perfect for picking up extra cash on the side&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

