&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reviewing and correcting&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;bounding boxes&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;around objects or people&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adjusting or refining&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;segmentation or masking areas&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;within images&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifying and&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;masking personally identifiable information (PII)&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;when required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensuring annotations follow detailed project guidelines and quality standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flagging unclear or incorrect labels for review&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Submitting completed annotation tasks through designated tools or platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
