&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Receive notifications about upcoming or ongoing data annotation projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review project details and decide whether you’d like to participate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete annotation tasks that match your skills and availability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gain access to future opportunities as new projects are launched&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
